website_summaries.verdict: They don’t call it Rainbow for nothing – these colorful, complete diet pellets are sure to catch your parakeet’s attention with their vibrant colors and crunchiness, but you’ll appreciate its healthy omega-3, vitamins, and minerals.
pros: Corn, wheat, and oats are the first 3 ingredients
Promotes brighter plumage and healthy heart, eyes, and brain function
cons: While your parakeet may find the rainbow of colors to be appetizing, it’s all from artificial food coloring

customer_reviews.title: Not my birds favorite but not a bad brand
customer_reviews.text: My parakeets are use to eating Zupreem brand but I decided to try something new because they were out of my birds favorite fruit blend. My first observation is Kaytee brand looks like Zupreem but the bits were bigger and it took a while for my birds to try it (but they a finicky bunch) and when they did try it, I saw them dipping the pieces in water as if they were too hard to eat. Evidently, they are eating it much slower than their favorite brand, but it just seem like they aren't enjoying it as much.

customer_reviews.title: Some parakeets won't eat it
customer_reviews.text: I liked the idea of not having to blow the hulls or the mess of the hulls BUT MY BIRDS WON'T EAT IT!! They are such whimpy birds! Sometimes they won't eat their "treats" because they are scared of it. After it has set there for a couple of days then they try it and "oh, it's not going to eat me so I will try it". They seem to eat around the pellets and eat the seed AFTER three days of NOT eating. I really wish my birds liked the pellets because it wouldn't be as messy. BTW, they won't eat ANYthing fresh and there is just so long you can leave "fresh" in the cage.

product_meta.title: Kaytee Exact Rainbow Parakeet & Lovebird Food, 2-Pound
product_meta.description:
Kaytee exact Rainbow Parakeet and Lovebird food is a premium extruded food and has been the recognized nutritional leader by avian nutritionists, veterinarians and breeders since its introduction over 25 years ago. Each nugget contains "exact nutrition" ensuring your bird gets exactly the right nutrition to produce better feathering, brighter colors and maintain excellent health. exact Rainbow is 100% consumable with no seed hulls or shells for less mess.

Kaytee understands that sharing your life with a pet bird is not only enjoyable but very enriching. Kaytee shows our love by ensuring we provide your pet bird with the best nutrition for a long and healthy life. 
With over 150 years of avian nutritional experience, it's no wonder why Kaytee is at the heart of every healthy feeding routine
feature_bullets: Omega 3's to support Brain and Heart Health
Enhances Skin & Feather health for vibrant, healthy plumage
Prebiotics and probiotics to support digestive health
100% consumable extruded nutrition with no shells or seed hulls
